data.description: Check out this beautiful 3bd/2.5ba home! Built in 2022, this home is in pristine condition! The first floor has an open feel and provides the perfect spot to host a gathering. The gorgeous kitchen features stainless steel appliances, a center island, and beautiful wood cabinets. Upstairs, you'll find a spacious primary suite with a walk-in closet and beautiful tile shower. Outside, you'll love the back porch as a hang out spot, featuring a privacy fence! Located just minutes from local shops, restaurants, and the Indianapolis Zoo! Ask co-listing agent about special financing for this property!
